  "description": "Quite an advanced, stylish and functional refrigerator, one of the most interesting features of which is that the user can change the front decorative panels. BeSpoke replaceable panels are presented in a wide range of shades and halftones. Otherwise, this is a fairly advanced two-chamber refrigerator with an inverter compressor, separate cooling circuits for the working chambers and a total useful capacity of 387 liters. The manufacturer has provided the ability to remotely control the operation of the device via Wi-Fi, as well as the ability to integrate equipment into the smart home system. The device is equipped with a Metal Cooling back wall, which stores cold. The Samsung BeSpoke RB38C7B6AB1 refrigerator boasts support for the CoolSelect + system, thanks to which the freezing zone can be turned into an additional cooling chamber with a temperature of +2 ° C. The refrigeration compartment has an Optimal Fresh + container, which creates ideal conditions for long-term storage of even perishable products. The maximum noise level generated during operation does not exceed 35 dB. The cooling and freezing chambers support the No Frost system technology, which protects the internal surfaces from ice formation.",
